Magic=

General Graardor can effectively be killed with [[Tumeken's shadow]], due to its extremely high accuracy and damage. However, due to its multiplicative effect, small downgrades in gear and levels can have a notable impact on damage output, and it is strongly recommended, if not essentially required, to have access to gear such as [[Ancestral robes]], an [[occult necklace]] and [[confliction gauntlets]].

Pairing the [[Eye of ayak]] with [[confliction gauntlets]] can be an effective strategy if freezing General Graardor due to the increased accuracy buff the [[confliction gauntlets]] provide as well.

While lower tier magic weapons can be used, they will be significantly less effective and should not be used except in combination with otherwise best-in-slot gear. With a 40% Earth spell weakness, [[Earth Wave]] or [[Earth Surge]] can be a competitive option for DPS, but being on the [[Standard spellbook]] means relying on other methods to restore health.

